The '''Roon Colonial Games''' was a series of games played on the planet [[Roon/Legends|Roon]]. Sentinels from all over Roon would come to see. Some competitors were [[Auren Yomm Baobab]], a friend of [[R2-D2/Legends|R2-D2]] and [[C-3PO/Legends|C-3PO]], and [[Bisad Koong]], the [[Governor/Legends|Imperial Governor]] of the [[Tawntoom]] province.

